    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>In your trance, you are on guard to those that would try and stand in your path. You call upon the inner power to unleash a reprisal. Spend your Zeal. The effects of the Zenith depends on the Zeal spent:</p><ul><li><p>1 Zeal: The creature takes 5 spirit damage.</p></li><li><p>2-3 Zeal: As 1 Zeal, but you also gain resistance 4 to the triggering damage.</p></li><li><p>4-5 Zeal: As above, but you also can make a Strike against the triggering creature if you can reach them with an attack.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Level (+4)</strong> The damage increases by 5 and the resistance increases by 2.</p>"
